        "text": "You hurl a loose, unattended object that is within range and that has 1 Bulk or less at the target. Make a spell attack roll against the target's AC. If you hit, you deal 2d6 bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage\u2014as appropriate for the object you hurled. No specific traits or magic properties of the hurled item affect the attack or the damage.",
